    "score" : 5,
    "last_activity_date" : 1455521188,
    "creation_date" : 1455521188,
    "answer_id" : 35403655,
    "question_id" : 35231291,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>My theory is that your java class file are using \"windows-1251\" encoding, and you need to set it \"UTF-8\".</p>\n\n<p>looks at the screenshots below.\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/Xp2xy.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/Xp2xy.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/2tmxa.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/2tmxa.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"></a></p>\n\n<p>To reset all files encoding, you can manually edit encodings.xml.\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/zfCm0.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/zfCm0.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"></a>\nYou can change the default file encoding in settings dialog.\n<a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/cHheD.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/cHheD.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"></a></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 297814,
      "reputation" : 26439,
      "user_id" : 603516,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 100,
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/40895ef337d0a2eb7d538f5f8b3e6d58?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "Vadzim",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/603516/vadzim"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 0,
    "last_activity_date" : 1604362605,
    "last_edit_date" : 1604362605,
    "creation_date" : 1511863872,
    "answer_id" : 47528892,
    "question_id" : 35231291,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>In my case, examining <code>System.out.textOut.out.se.cs</code> in debug hinted that IDEA <a href=\"https://intellij-support.jetbrains.com/hc/en-us/community/posts/206423669-Junit-Maven-surefire-plugin-settings\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">picked up maven surefire arguments</a> for every JUnit Run Configuration:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-xml prettyprint-override\"><code>&lt;plugin&gt;\n    &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;/groupId&gt;\n    &lt;artifactId&gt;maven-surefire-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n    &lt;configuration&gt;\n        &lt;!-- force 7-bit default encoding to ensure that nothing depends on it --&gt;\n        &lt;argLine&gt;-Dfile.encoding=ASCII&lt;/argLine&gt;\n    &lt;/configuration&gt;\n&lt;/plugin&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<p>I've resolved this by adding <code>-Didea.maven.surefire.disable.argLine=true</code> to the <a href=\"https://intellij-support.jetbrains.com/hc/en-us/articles/206544869-Configuring-JVM-options-and-platform-properties\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">idea64.exe.vmoptions</a> file.</p>\n<p>See also: <a href=\"https://www.jetbrains.com/help/idea/configuring-output-encoding.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://www.jetbrains.com/help/idea/configuring-output-encoding.html</a>.</p>\n"
  }, {
