      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Thanks!! This is also accessible from <code>Help &gt;  Edit custom VM options...</code> then restart IntelliJ. I literally tried everything: changing encoding settings everywhere in IntelliJ, changing JVM options set by properties file, build.gradle file, IntelliJ, run configuration, environment variable, etc. Also tried changing system wide encoding nothing worked but this."
