    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>This works for me.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Close your intellij idea</li>\n<li>Search and open file idea.exe.vmoptions inside idea installed, for example: &quot;C:\\Program Files\\JetBrains\\IntelliJ IDEA 2018.3.2\\bin&quot;.\nAfter add next line: -Dfile.encoding=UTF-8</li>\n<li>(Optional) if you have file idea64.exe.vmoptions, add the same line too.</li>\n<li>Start your intellij idea.</li>\n</ol>\n"
