    "body" : "<p>You may have modified the wrong file，</p>\n\n<p>not : <code>C:\\Program Files\\JetBrains\\IntelliJ IDEA xxxx\\bin\\idea64.exe.vmoptions</code></p>\n\n<p>should be: <code>C:\\Users\\USER_NAME\\.IntelliJIdeaxxxx\\config\\idea64.exe.vmoptions</code></p>\n\n<p>you can add both <code>-Dfile.encoding=UTF-8</code> and <code>-Dconsole.encoding=UTF-8</code></p>\n"
