    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>IntelliJ IDEA uses the operating system's shell internally as the console. In Windows that's Command Prompt. So if adding...</p>\n<pre><code>-Dconsole.encoding=UTF-8\n-Dfile.encoding=UTF-8\n</code></pre>\n<p>... to your VM Options under <code>Help -&gt; Edit Custom VM Options</code> doesn't help, ensure your shell supports UTF-8 characters in the first place.</p>\n"
