    "body" : "<p>The garbled characters have been resolved with the following settings.\n(IntelliJ IDEA Community 2022.2)</p>\n<pre><code> - Build, Execution, Deployment &gt; Build Tools &gt; Runner &gt; Environment vairables.\n - JAVA_TOOL_OPTIONS=-Dfile.encoding=UTF8\n</code></pre>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/17xyd.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">ScreenShot</a></p>\n"
