      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Thank you, this is what actually helped in my case! You may also want to do the same for stderr: <code>System.setErr(PrintStream(FileOutputStream(FileDescriptor.er&zwnj;&#8203;r), true, Charsets.UTF_8))</code>"
